videos.description: Wichita State forward Rashard Kelly's sweet dish leads to dunk for Shaquille Morris.
videos.headline: Great pass sets up emphatic dunk for Shockers

videos.description: Wichita State swings the ball around and Shaquille Morris hits Conner Frankamp for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Shockers' ball movement leads to 3

videos.description: UConn forward Kwintin Williams gets the lob from Jalen Adams and throws it down for the jam.
videos.headline: Huskies' Williams shows off vertical with alley-oop

videos.description: Wichita State's Rashard Kelly drives to the hoop and finds Shaquille Morris who finishes with the slam.
videos.headline: Shockers' Kelly draws defense, hits Morris for jam

videos.description: The Huskies try to corral the ball, but run into each other and end up throwing the ball off their own teammate.
videos.headline: UConn players can't handle rebound

videos.description: Huskies guard Antwoine Anderson tosses up the lob to Kwintin Williams who throws it down.
videos.headline: UConn connects on one-handed alley-oop dunk.

videos.description: Kevin Brown and John Thompson III break down Wichita State's win over UConn and the tough schedule ahead for the Shockers.
videos.headline: Thompson: This is the Wichita State team we've been looking for
